remove|CXX_STD=CXX11|from|src/Makevars.in|||

3. From the|rquantlib|parent directory, fire up R and execute|, 
library(devtools) install() library(RQuantLib) 
getHolidayList("UnitedStates", as.Date("2018-12-01"), 
as.Date("2019-01-02")) |
